 "html": "<p>Ek was lus vir lekker klewerige, vinger-af-lek, stroperige hoender.  Jy sal mond en hande moet was na jy dit geeet het.  Die suiker kan jy verminder as jy iets nie so soets wil eet nie.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-060.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1540\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 060\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-060-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>BESTANDELE:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 koppie tamatiesous<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-009.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1530\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 009\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-009-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>1 koppie bruinsuiker<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-001.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1528\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 001\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-001-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>1 koppie heuning<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-011.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1531\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 011\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-011-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>1/2koppie sojasous<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-013.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1532\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 013\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-013-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>4 knoffelhuisies<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-018.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1534\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 018\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-018-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOU:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>meng al die bestandele vir die sous en kook vir so 6 minute op die stoof<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-020.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1535\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 020\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-020-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>gooi die hoender en sous in n mengbak en meng goed<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-025.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1536\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 025\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-025-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>plaas dit in n oondbak en bak dit vir 1 uur by 180 grade Celsius<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-029.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1537\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 029\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-029-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>draai dit om en om en om gedurende die proses<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-053.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1541\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 053\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-053-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Dit blink. Dis heerlik. Dit vra vir nog.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-043.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1543\" alt=\"MARINDA BLOG 043\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MARINDA-BLOG-043-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
